      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer David${action:Stand01}<BR>H-help?! You have misunderstood me!<BR>All I did was to give you the opportunity to work for <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT>! That's what I meant!</html>]]></talk_question>
