      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-a" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I've brought it on behalf of Argenta.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I feel the faint energy of the Black Dragon.<BR>Do you have the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Core Fragments</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-b" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay. And I also had a question.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I believe she sent them to me to help me recover.<BR>They're dangerous for you so don't touch them too much.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-c" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You ask Adventurer David's question.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>A question...? What is it?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-c" image="QM_black_Dragon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-d" mid="113" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="112"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>So you want to know what happened 50 years ago.<BR>Five factions merged to fight the <FONT color=#a82424>Black Dragon</FONT> that time.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Geraint speaks without any emotion)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
