      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-f" mid="120" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="119"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>And…<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Velskud</FONT>'s Cassius Kingdom Knights.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-f" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-g" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are you talking about Dark Elf Elena?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I was the leader. Argenta acted independently to check on the <FONT color=#a82424>Red Army</FONT>.<BR>And then, she had to fight a <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Elf</FONT> who was attacking the soldiers at the rear so she couldn't join us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-g" image="QM_Ellena.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-h" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>That's right. Argenta destroyed <FONT color=#a82424>Elena</FONT>'s monsters almost completely.<BR>And when the Black Dragon was defeated, the people began to call the six who led each faction as the Six Heroes.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-h" image="QN_six_heroes_silhouette.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-i" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>That's why there are no records about <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT>. Most of the people don't even know that she exists.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n216_geraint_wounded-5-i" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>Only humans obsess over titles and records.<BR>Because of the brevity of their lives, they covet things that would remain in history for a long time.<BR>Such things are meaningless to me and <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
