      <talk_answer link_index="n213_slave_david-6-a" mid="57" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer David${action:Stand01}<BR>I was just expecting you to arrive now! Ha. Ha. Ha.<BR>I assume you met <FONT color=#a82424>Geraint</FONT>, right?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n213_slave_david-6-a" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n213_slave_david-6-b" mid="59" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell him what Geraint said)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer David$<BR>So how come the <FONT color=#7e12d2>beautiful </FONT>, <FONT color=#382000><FONT color=#a94407>lovely</FONT>, and </FONT><FONT color=#086171>ultra perfect</FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>Argenta</FONT> is not one of the Six Heroes?! Did you find out why? Tell me!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n213_slave_david-6-b" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n213_slave_david-6-c" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(He is praising enthusiastically)</html>]]></talk_answer>
